  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Point <math alttext=\"upper F\"><mi>F</mi>\n</math> lies on a unit circle in the <em>xy</em>-plane and has coordinates <math alttext=\"left parenthesis 1 comma 0 right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>. Point <math alttext=\"upper G\"><mi>G</mi>\n</math> is the center of the circle and has coordinates <math alttext=\"left parenthesis 0 comma 0 right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>. Point <math alttext=\"upper H\"><mi>H</mi>\n</math> also lies on the circle and has coordinates <math alttext=\"left parenthesis negative 1 comma y right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfenced></math>, where <math alttext=\"y\"><mi>y</mi>\n</math> is a constant. Which of the following could be the positive measure of angle <math alttext=\"upper F upper G upper H\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>F</mi>\n\t<mi>G</mi>\n\t<mi>H</mi>\n</mrow>\n</math>, in radians?</p>",
